articles.title: Agricultural import policy changes affect local farmers
articles.description: Agricultural import policy changes affect local farmers. Agricultural Import Policy continues to dominate Kenyan policy discourse as stakeholders weigh in on the implications for ordinary citizens.
articles.content: Agricultural import policy changes affect local farmers. The Agricultural Import Policy has been a subject of intense debate across Kenya. Analysts say the policy will have significant implications for the agriculture sector. Various stakeholders including civil society groups, business associations, and county governments have expressed diverse opinions on the matter.
